==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Colossal
<hw>Co*los"sal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>colossal</ets>, L. <ets>colosseus</ets>. See
<er>Colossus</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of enormous size; gigantic;
huge; <as>as, a <ex>colossal</ex> statue</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A
<xex>colossal</xex> stride.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Motley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Sculpture & Painting)</fld> <def>Of a size larger
than heroic. See <er>Heroic</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colossean</ent>⟦br⟧
